  "text": "To implement the real-time cooperation among AVAs, we propose a three-layered interaction architecture. In each layer, parallel processes exchange different kinds of information for effective cooperation. To realize a real-time information exchange and processing, we employ the dynamic memory architecture [CITATION_1] . The dynamic interaction in each layer allows the total system to track multiple moving objects under complicated dynamic situations in the real world. ",
